Author: fishonthesun
Text: You said you have seen a few therapists- don't give up on that. For a lot of people, it takes a while. Also, I dont know anything besides what you've said, but you may need to consider the possibility that you are mentally holding yourself back. Maybe you don't even realize it. But you may be blocking your own attempts to recover- whether it be not being honest with yourself or just knowingly lying to doctors.  I hope that wasnt offensive, it just seems that you are really struggling and I dont know if anyone's ever discussed that as a potential problem with you.  I hope you can find someone who helps you <3
